"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Chuyan village is an extremely primitive and backward village. When she first married here, she looked beautiful and moving. I don't know how many people she had been fascinated by.\\n\\n \\n\\nThe day before the winter solstice this year, the sun touched the whole village warm and comfortable like a mother's hand. Birds jumped around on the willow branches by the stream, pecking the grass and their beloved feathers. The woman came back from her distant mother's house. The smile on her face was like the rising sun. She gently pulled out a package of flower seeds from her arms and sowed them like rain in the rice field on the Bank of the river.\\n\\n \\n\\n\\\"I must change this poor and backward mountain village.\\\" The woman thought.\\n\\n \\n\\nThe captain shouted angrily, \\\"this is a place to plant rice, not flowers and grass!\\\"\\n\\n \\n\\n“这是黄芪，有生育能力！” 她咯咯地笑着，宛如清澈的山泉。\\n\\n \\n\\n次年，春风拂面，这些田野中的紫云疯狂地生长着。一夜之间，百花盛开，像一朵低飞的紫云。船长不信，就叫人把紫云英从地里拉出来；但是这些地里的庄稼长得很好。\\n\\n \\n\\n村民们目瞪口呆。从此，紫云英年年燃烧，填满了整片田地，山村一次次在丰收中微笑弯腰。\\n\\n \\n\\n村民们仍然习惯于传统的耕作方式。\\n\\n \\n\\n三十年后。曾经，她长得很丑，但爱花种花的习惯没有改变。\\n\\n \\n\\n她老了，老到只剩下五颗牙齿了。她种了很多花，包括牡丹、牡丹和百合。夕阳西下，她总是喜欢一个人看花开又谢。她所坐的石凳旁边，也出现了一朵花，而那些花则是扎根于深深的泥土之中。\\n\\n \\n\\n后来，一位老中医路过，对端坐的丑女说，这些丹皮、白芍、百合都是上品药材，可以卖不少钱。老妪带着儿孙们种了更多的药材，那年家里发了大财；夕阳西下，老太婆静静地坐在门前，数着这些盛开的花朵。\",\"timestamp\":1639148421,\"title\":\"CHU  YAN\"},\"digest\":\"4W-Jh-lDoqWfIteeLFatT66ZGRSh16aW8hKi6byfIB4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8A5648Bf0C62868749b4919861E3F455df576b97\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"atOT4FMSzMQVumMAGdkEBbme0Acd1oGdqFxUjeSASYs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ez3N6345Uckl1s8SnXIV5pFbnMhZIlARUKGGFKpgnpI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"0TI9aLtlDp5hB19hLY3cCG2JU1_1lBDUCkrY8HZIhXbwEQIuUvL1fOCD8Ji846Z66N09LQVZ3G7jWgIoOwTVeQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x38a15e1b66b2f00d7d59e4b4ff33a9684eb34643f5671b5266d629d78f85495840b2e762543b7b0b336d8711da34ac65f04af